gameTextList = ["[Chara A]\n", "* charaA\n", "Ok, {charaB}, seems like we're all set up!\n", "* charaB\n", "I, {charaB}, thank you for your help, {charaA}\n", "* charaA\n", "Byes\n", "[Chara A outtake]\n", "* charaA\n", "cool\n", "[Chara B]\n", "* charaB\n", "really\n", "before 'It works'\n", "@ [It works]\n", "[It works]\n", "It does work indeed\n", "[Chara B HP]\n", "* charaA\n", "{charaB}, I am about to increase your energy!\n", "*\n", "* charaB\n", "Thank you, {charaA}\n", "[Test YN]\n", "%\n", "Do you want to quit?\n", "& YES\n", "@ [Chara A]\n", "& NO\n", "@ [Chara B]\n", "%", "[doomclock intro]\n", "*\n", "Ah, the doomsday clock. When the hand reaches 12, the whole of creation will end.\n", "[doom bugle clue]\n", "*\n", "Don't worry about doomsday, {luc}.\n", "As long as the 7 trumpets are not played, all's right with the world.\n", "[heaven gate 1]\n", "* luc\n", "Outta my way! I need to talk to God.\n", "*\n", "By appointment only, {luc}.\n", "[heaven gate 2]\n", "*\n", "The way you go about creating trouble, {luc}, you're lucky not to have been cast onto the depths of Hell!\n", "[le intro]\n", "*\n", "{luc}, you should quit your rebellious ways and serve God like the rest of us angels.\n", "[temple doom intro]\n", "*\n", "This is where the 7 Doomsday trumpets are housed at: The Temple of Doom! \n", "* luc\n", "Shouldn't it be the \"Temple of Doomsday\" then?\n", "*\n", "If you can make that fit on the marquee, please be my guest!\n", "[chili peppers]\n", "*\n", "\"...the city I live in: The city of angels. Lonely as I am, together we cry!\"\n", "* luc\n", "What's that nonsense about?\n", "*\n", "Sorry, I'm just writing some lyrics...\n", "[david lynch]\n", "*\n", "\"In Heaven, everything is fine. You got your good things and I've got mine.\"\n", "* luc\n", "What are YOU babbling on about?\n", "*\n", "We've got a little poetry competition going on. We want to know who's the best wordsmith around here.\n", "[apocalypse etymology]\n", "*\n", "If \"Apocalypse\" means revelation, is the upcoming Doomsday the ultimate source of knowledge?\n", "[game start]\n", "* \n", "\"In the beginning was the Word, and the Word was with God, and the Word was God.\" \\n -- John 1,1\n", "[luc outta jail]\n", "* mic\n", "How did you get out, {luc}? Your confinement wasn't supposed to end until the next millenia!\n", "* luc\n", "That's none of your business, {mic}!\n", "And what are you going to do? Arrest me again? For what?\n", "Searching for enlightenment? Maybe I have found the light already\n", "* mic\n", "Where you find \"enlightenment\", I see nothing but heresy.\n", "Why don't you just fall in line and worship the Maker like the rest of us?\n", "* luc\n", "I'm not planning to fall. In line or at all! I will rise above you all. You'll see.\n", "* mic\n", "Oh, {luc}, one day you'll find out that every uprising is leads to a downfall.", "[Heaven Assembly]\n", "* luc\n", "Angels! I used the Doomsday bugle to summon you here...\n", "* mic\n", "{luc}! It's only supposed to be used in case of emergency!\n", "* luc\n", "Well, thanks to my discovery, there shall be no Doomsday any more.\n", "* mic\n", "That's not your prerrogative, {luc}!\n", "* luc\n", "Oh, I beg to differ, my dear {mic}.\n", "You all know me as the most beautiful and powerful of all angels in creation.\n", "But what you don't know is that I'm also the smartest...\n", "* mic\n", "Don't forget humble too, {luc}!\n", "* luc\n", "Don't get your toga in a twist, {mic}\n", "I found out that what we call reality is an illusion. But allow me to demonstrate that...\n", "* \n", "What IS that?\n", "What are those squiggly lines?\n", "I think it's the Matrix!\n", "* nerd\n", "Hmm, it appears to be some sort of videogame's source code. Maybe an RPG. Definitely written in Python 3. \n", "Just look at the 'print' statements with the enclosing brackets\n", "* luc\n", "Shut up, nerd! You're ruining my monologue!\n", "These are WORDS. This is the source of creation. \n", "I say we take those words and write a better story than the one we've got so far!\n", "I say we create a world without angels and archangels.\n", "Without an almighty tyrant ruling over us.\n", "A place where each of us is a god in their own right!\n", "Who is with me?\n", "* mic\n", "That does it, {luc}! You're inciting a riot!\n", "* luc\n", "You're such a teacher's pet, {mic}. Bring it on!\n", "[luc champion]\n", "* luc\n", "$(set_flag, [is_satan, True])\n", "From now on, I am {luc}, The Prince of Darkness!\n", "* nerd\n", "You mean, like Ozzy Osbourne?\n", "* luc\n", "I have no idea what you're talking about, nerd!\n", "As my first act as The Prince of Darkness, I shall venture forth into Chaos alone and find out more about this New World that is being created now.", "[project eva]\n", "* luc\n", "How's our code-breaking effort going? Have you figured out what God and his stupid angels are up to now?\n", "* nerd\n", "It's a bit unclear at the moment but it seems that He is creating a new creature. Not as cool as us, angels...\n", "* luc\n", "Demons. We are demons now. That's the name we're going with.\n", "* nerd\n", "Right, demons. So, this new being won't have wings like us. Or our amazing powers.\n", "* luc\n", "Do you know the project's name?\n", "* nerd\n", "Project Eva... maybe Eve. And I think there's some other dude too. Something like 'Alan'?\n", "* luc\n", "Alan & Eva?\n", "* nerd\n", "Well, the Alan part I'm not 100% sure but the Eva bit I think is right.\n", "* luc\n", "Project Eva? Sounds like a secret weapon to me...\n", "* nerd\n", "Maybe it's a giant robot! That would be so cool...\n", "* luc\n", "Where do you come up with these stupid ideas?\n", "* nerd\n", "Before I became a demon, I wanted to make comic books. When that failed, I turned to animation. When that also failed, I started making games.\n", "My dream one day is to make a 3D JRPG about our struggle to perfect creation and call it \"Satan's Quest\"!\n", "* luc\n", "I regret asking this question.\n", "[hell shop]\n", "% What are we buying today?\n", "& produto 1 $10\n", "$(buy, [1, 10])\n", "& produto 2 $5\n", "$(buy, [2, 5])\n", "& produto 3 $1\n", "$(buy, [3, 1])\n", "%\n", "[beelzebub]\n", "* bee\n", "I am {bee}, Lord of the Flies! \n", "I know I smell bad but if I take a shower, I'll be a rather lonely lord\n", "[elle]\n", "* elle\n", "I'm {elle} and I won't let you through!\n", "[ee]\n", "* ee\n", "I'm {ee} and I'm ending the error of your ways!\n", "[gee]\n", "* gee \n", "Geez wheez! I'm {gee} and your journey is adjourned!\n", "[eye]\n", "* eye\n", "I am {eye}... I mean, me. No, wait! Let's just fight!\n", "[oh]\n", "* oh\n", "I am {oh}!\n", "* luc\n", "IMO? \"In my opinion\"?\n", "* oh\n", "That will do: In my opinion, you're dead!\n", "[ann]\n", "* ann\n", "I'm {ann}.\n", "@ [ann question]\n", "[ann question]\n", "% Any questions?\n", "& YES\n", "@ [ann yes]\n", "& NO\n", "@ [ann no]\n", "%\n", "[ann yes]\n", "* ann\n", "Well, I don't care. You'll die now anyway!\n", "[ann no]\n", "* ann\n", "Good, let's fight then!\n", "[gang warning]\n", "* nerd\n", "{luc}, I have to warn you that there's a bounty on your head\n", "* luc\n", "Which demon would be so stupid to threaten me?\n", "* nerd\n", "Not one demon... Six! Six! Six!\n", "* luc\n", "Six hundred and sixty six? I like the sound of that!\n", "* nerd\n", "Ah, no, no. It's just six of them.\n", "* luc\n", "Just half a dozen? Why do you bother me with such meager numbers?\n", "[behemoth]\n", "* beh\n", "I'm in hell. Soaking in tar. Sticky but exfoliating.\n", "My skin feels like perfect peach now.", "[lili pre fight]\n", "* luc\n", "I have finally managed to track you down, {lil} You must tell me where God's new creation is!\n", "* lil\n", "So you're God's most beautiful angel? Not much of a looker in my book.\n", "* luc\n", "I'm no angel!\n", "* lil\n", "Neither am I, darling! Prepare to die!\n", "[lili post fight]\n", "* lil\n", "Impossible! You have defeated me and my beloved dinosaurs!\n", "* luc\n", "Enough small talk! Tell me where I can find this \"Project Eva\"!\n", "* lil\n", "You mean Adam & Eve? What can you do to them? They are under angelic protection around the clock.\n", "* luc\n", "You tell me where they are and I will corrupt God's creation from within.\n", "* lil\n", "You want to destroy them? Fine, they live in the garden of Eden. \n", "If you go through this exit behind me, you'll get there.\n", "Hmm, are we having an eclipse?\n", "[dino entrance]\n", "*\n", "Welcome to the Dinosaur Den\n", "a.k.a. The Lost World\n", "[dino meet]\n", "*\n", "What sort of strange dinosaur are you?\n", "You look like a weird breed of Triceratops and Pterodactyl...\n", "[dino mammal]\n", "% Are you a mammal?\n", "& Of course!\n", "@ [is mammal]\n", "& Hell no!\n", "@ [is not mammal]\n", "& What's that?\n", "@ [what is mammal]\n", "%\n", "[is mammal]\n", "*\n", "So get out of my sight, you furry!\n", "[is not mammal]\n", "*\n", "Thank the Great Lizard!\n", "Mammals are furry, flea-ridden and reek of milk.\n", "Not elegant like us, avian-like reptiles!\n", "[what is mammal]\n", "*\n", "A mammal is tiny creature that feeds on our eggs.\n", "Trust me, they will never rule the Earth!", "[edens gate]\n", "*\n", "Halt! Who goes there?\n", "@ [edens gate choice 1]\n", "[edens gate choice 1]\n", "% I'm...\n", "& just a snake.\n", "@ [edens gate fail]\n", "& {luc}\n", "@ [edens gate choice 2]\n", "%\n", "[edens gate fail]\n", "*\n", "Wait a minute! I think know who you are...\n", "* luc\n", "Me?\n", "@ [edens gate choice 1]\n", "[edens gate choice 2]\n", "*\n", "Yeah, right! You don't fool me, you silly serpent!\n", "[eden greeting]\n", "*\n", "Welcome back to the Garden of Eden!\n", "[eden question]\n", "*\n", "Why do you keep running off? Aren't you happy here?\n", "[gorilla]\n", "*\n", "Me? I'm not Eve. But i can see why you mistook us.\n", "We're probably cousins or something...\n", "[lion king]\n", "*\n", "Eve? She has a mane like mine, but her body is hairless and she lacks a tail.\n", "Don't mention it to her though. Maybe she has a fur condition.\n", "[chimp]\n", "*\n", "No idea where Eve is but could you help me get the Apple of Knowledge?\n", "If I eat from it, I'll be smarter than Adam & Eve!\n", "[wolf]\n", "*\n", "I love sheep. They're so nice to talk to.\n", "[sheep]\n", "*\n", "Wolves are so cool. I can't imagine a world where we're not friends.\n", "[hippo]\n", "* luc\n", "{beh}! How did you get here?\n", "* \n", "{beh}? I'm just a hippo."]